models

Class Coordinate

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.Coordinate

  • public class Coordinate
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a combination of two properties X and Y. Imagine a grid of cells that have the coordinates X and Y. In this case, field X corresponds to the number of row in grid, and field Y corresponds to the number of column in grid.
    Since:
    Tetris 1.0
    Author:
    Daniil Kachur
